data.description: Welcome to your coastal retreat! This delightful 3-bed, 2-bath home is perfectly situated offering an ideal blend of comfort and convenience. Packed with desirable features, this property is a must-see for those looking for a primary, secondary, or an investment home. Step inside to discover an expansive living area open to an eat-in kitchen. The kitchen boasts stunning granite countertops and abundant storage space. The 3 bedrooms are bathed in natural light. The primary suite is a private sanctuary, complete with an en-suite bathroom. Outside, the fenced backyard guarantees a secure space for outdoor activities, barbecues, or simply enjoying your own slice of paradise. The 2-car attached garage provides both convenience and storage solutions. But the true allure of this property lies in its location - a short drive from the beach. Plus, Moody Gardens, a Galveston staple, is just a stone's throw away, offering entertainment and educational experiences for all ages.
